Important notes for Hands-on attendees 
Before coming to the hands-on lab, you should make the environment ready:

For Windows users:
. Laptop with Windows 10 Operating System
路 Install Visual Studio 2019 : https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/vs/
路 Install Azure Sphere SDK : https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure-sphere/install/install-sdk#azure-sphere-sdk-preview-for-visual-studio

For Ubuntu users:
. Laptop with Ubuntu LTS 18.04
. Install VS code
. Install Azure Sphere SDK for VS code

All:
路 Get a Microsoft Account (skip if you already have an account) : https://account.microsoft.com/account
路 Create an Azure free account (skip if you already did) : https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/free/
 
